        "content": "<p>bjorn3 <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13383#issuecomment-4458881387\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13383\">PR #13383</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Maybe put this behind a feature flag? This wouldn't be usable for rustc_codegen_cranelift as it doesn't allow writing an LSDA.</p>\n<p>On arm64 Mach-O it should be possible to emit <code>__TEXT,__eh_frame</code> by the way: <a href=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rustc_codegen_cranelift/pull/1634\">https://github.com/rust-lang/rustc_codegen_cranelift/pull/1634</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
