    {
        "content": "<p>HueCodes <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13383#issuecomment-4462895982\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13383\">PR #13383</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>@bjorn3 thanks. Done: default-on \"unwind\" Cargo feature mirroring cranelift-codegen's \"unwind\", with gimli and ObjectBuilder::unwind_info both gated behind it, so cg_clif drops the dep and API via default-features = false. Kept Mach-O scoped out for now (wrong-reloc risk); TODO left pointing at<br>\ncg_clif#1634.</p>\n</blockquote>",
