    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"memo\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4dd\" role=\"img\" title=\"memo\">:memo:</span> fitzgen submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13383#pullrequestreview-4312131731\">PR review</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks! I think we could clean up the boundary between <code>cfg(feature = \"unwind\")</code> vs <code>cfg(not(feature = \"unwind\"))</code> a bit.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 595882299,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1779124104
    },
    {
